    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1932-02-15T15:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1932-02-15T15:00:00-05:00" n="365"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d365">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/4210: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Switzerland (<persName corresp="#p_WHR1"
                            type="from">Wilson</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Geneva</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-02-15T21:00:00+01:00"
                            >February 15, 1932—9 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received February 15—4:45 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>22. A meeting of the Twelve will be held tomorrow morning to discuss a
                    declaration proposed by the Secretary General which is called an appeal to Japan
                    but which is more vigorous in tone than this appellation would indicate.<note
                        n="48" xml:id="d365fn48">With reference to this paragraph, the Secretary of
                        State replied in telegram No. 15, February 15, 7 p.m., “This information is
                        noted here with gratification.”</note>
                </p>
                <p>After this discussion the Twelve will, if time permits, decide on China’s demand
                    for the summoning of the Assembly.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_WHR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
